* ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
* B1700 MIL Test Program 4 — Arithmetic via Function Box
* Tests: LIT, MOVE to X/Y, read SUM, conditional skip
* ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
*
* The function box automatically computes SUM = X + Y.
*
* Expected result: X = 25, Y = 17, T = SUM = 42
*

START       LIT 25 TO X                  * X ← 25
            LIT 17 TO Y                  * Y ← 17
            MOVE SUM TO T                * T ← SUM (= X + Y = 42)
            HALT
